map.name: A Diverse World
map.description: Welcome to the original better world map! Explore the World with more than 50,000 hand-picked pinpointable locations from all the countries available on Google Street View! This map should contain no blurry picture or photospheres for a better game experience. | The legacy 2.x version is still available here: https://www.geoguessr.com/maps/5f6a66b182e9640001a0872d | Please read for more details and how to report a bad location: https://goo.gl/Gj76EF〔50778 loc.︱v3.1︱2020/11/09〕
